
<slide>
<heading>Supplementary Exams
Suplementary Exams are only available to people who
<itemize>
<item> are absent from the Final Exam with <i>good reason</i> <br>
	<small>(good = documented, serious, clearly affects ability to do exam)</small>
<item> have performed well during the rest of the semester
</itemize>
If you are awarded a Supp Exam ...
<itemize>
<item> you <b>must</b> make yourself available for it
	<small>(mid January)</small>
<item> non-attendance at the Supp <$><Rightarrow></$> mark of 0 for the exam
</itemize>
</slide>

